] Jiang X, Williams KM, Liauw WS, et al. "Effect of ginkgo and ginger on the pharmacokinetics and pharmacodynamics of warfarin in healthy subjects." Br J Clin Pharmacol 59 (2005):  425-32[18] Jayasekera N, Moghal A, Kashif F, Karalliedde L "Herbal medicines and postoperative haemorrhage." Anaesthesia 60 (2005):  725-6[19] Wolf HR "Does Ginkgo biloba special extract EGb 761 provide additional effects on coagulation and bleeding when added to acetylsalicylic acid 500 mg daily?" Drugs R D 7 (2006):  163-72', 'Rivastigmine, Galantamine, Aducanumab, Memantine, Tacrine', 'Rabeprazole, Misoprostol, Chondroitin sulfate, Glucosamine, Esomeprazole, Tolazoline, Rabeprazole, Dimethyl sulfoxide, Salicylic acid, Fluocinolone acetonide, Cortisone, More', 1767369485);
